{"tid":1213792,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阮兆祥：示威破壞某啲香港人生活","createTime":"2019-06-13T02:46:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T07:03:15.000Z","uid":10014,"like":7,"dislike":152,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ae0571d3a5e16a2293435b1358dacf31aaf67854","tid":1213792,"uid":10014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:46:30.000Z","msg":"立法會原定今日就《逃犯條例》修例二讀，不少熱心巿民今日響應罷工罷巿罷課，到金鐘政總外示威，反對修例，最後跟警察發生衝突。有人選擇站出來保護香港的同時，亦可以有不同選擇，實屬無可厚非。<br />\n<br />\n祥仔阮兆祥就選擇了跟男友人逛街，今日下午5時許，見到祥仔在又一城一商場跟友人在商場內找舖頭，最後去了一間連鎖精品店。花了大約20分鐘左右便完成揀禮物及付款離開。他在等電梯時接受《蘋果》訪問，被問到對條例的看法，祥仔說：「有啲支持(內容)有啲反對(內容)。當然清場係應該嘅，因為始終可能會破壞到某啲香港人生活，我支持佢哋用一個比較溫和理性嘅方式去對待呢件事情，兩面都係我覺得，我期待住一個好嘅成果，我諗無論企喺邊一方，身為香港人都係愛香港，希望香港係好嘅，希望兩面都能夠互相體諒。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190612/59708444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708444&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=1510c789\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190612%2F59708444&h=052c3cf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20190612/59708444</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">琴日有無人見到阿祥仔幫手呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d9e7f268aec8a85ba1a8570e36cae2d18bdc0e58","tid":1213792,"uid":17641,"like":144,"dislike":1,"score":143,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:47:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>咁你尋日又去衝</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7981b925b4af053ac8764336172dc1baa2b2c607","tid":1213792,"uid":236368,"lik